{"type": "article", "id": 13992, "title": "NIKEiD Prime Fleece 系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-26T07:50:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 58, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607114958BgCDpdKQ4AHohjkU.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t进入秋季，天气开始转凉。NIKEiD 最近新推出了 Prime Fleece 系列，为经典的鞋款提供了新的抓绒面料，质地前所未有的温暖和柔软，且更加轻便。新系列包含了 Air Huarache，Roshe Run 和女生专属的 Juvenate 鞋款。新系列将于 8 月 27 日正式发售，<a href=\"http://www.nike.com/us/en_us/launch/c/2015-08/nikeid-prime-fleece-collection\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261416380IqYfg8FrBpZKs4a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141638Hs0eISzCDioMr3tF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141639BIFGpNmg0XiYklsy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141639H3mpexWlifOkIDVL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}